\FX[FFF]\AA[F]\FFF[1012Furea_0000]With this, the mysterious disappearances should stop. We'll
leave the rest to the Justice Knights' rescue team. Now,
let's return home♪

\FX[FFF]\AA[FFF]\FFF[1012Furea_0005]\N<Flare>I have a really bad feeling about what lies ahead. Are we
prepared...

(I have a bad feeling about what's ahead... I can't go on
with my stomach like this...)

\FX[F]\AA[F]\M[InR]\F[1012Furea_0012]\N<Flare>Pure Flame, arriving!! I will burn your evil deeds to
ashes!!
\FX[F]\AA[FFFF]\MMMM[jump]\F[1012Furea_0012]\FFFF[4010goblin]\N<Goblin>From yourself, you will bear our children!!
\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0011]\FFFF[4010goblin]\N<Flare>B-bear children... What are you talking about!?

\FX[F]\AA[F]\M[no]\F[1012Furea_0011]\FFFF[4010goblin]\N<Flare>Gather... So, you were indeed the cause of the nearby
disappearances!!

\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0018]\FFFF[4010goblin]\N<Flare>And, by that way of speaking, the people who were kidnapped
are surely still...!?

\FX[F]\AA[FFFF]\MMMM[jump]\F[1012Furea_0018]\FFFF[4010goblin]\N<Goblin>Gehgehgeh. You will become such. Our baby, soon, you will
bear!!

\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0017]\FFFF[4010goblin]\N<Flare>S-such a thing, I will absolutely not allow it!! Pure Flame,
you cannot lose!!

\FX[F]\AA[FF]\F[1012Furea_0018]\FFFF[4010goblin]Heh heh heh!! The female has returned!! Violate her!! ＜If
you are defeated twice, you will proceed to a BAD END＞

\FX[FFF]\AA[F]\FFF[1012Furea_0000]This should stop the mysterious disappearances. We'll leave
the rest to the Justice Knights' rescue team. Now, let's
return home♪
